_aChangeLog.text: added some stuff to fix bot behavior, added minor changes to the map, and added some more screenshots.

_sText:
This is a map of my house that I made because i wanted to.
It includes a full navigation mesh because its epic.

To install: place the de_raid.bsp into C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps
and place the de_raid_custom folder in C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\custom

Then the map should work probably.

IMPORTANT: includes my cat
